ComicInfo.Title: Prep and Landing: Mansion: Impossible; Law of the Jungle
ComicInfo.Summary:
Prep and Landing: Mansion: Impossible: Two Christmas elves attempt to deliver presents to the Avengers mansion.
Law of the Jungle: The Fantastic Four team up with Black Panther to catch a ring of smugglers stealing Vibranium from Wakanda.
